description-en_US-print:
Capture the world in brilliant 3D. Now with Toshiba’s new, amazingly affordable CAMILEO® Z100 3D Camcorder, you can easily shoot 3D video in 1080p Full HD, and create amazing movies.

Got a 3D TV or a 3D laptop? The CAMILEO® Z100 3D Camcorder lets you create your own 3D content—in 1080p Full HD—at a fraction of the price of more expensive camcorders. With a glasses-free 3D touchscreen you can shoot Dad’s birthday party right from the camera and comfortably watch it again in 3D on the camera screen.

Ready to go big? Send your new videos to the 3D big screen with an included Mini HDMI® cable. When it comes to editing, this traditional form factor camcorder certainly holds its own. On-screen video trimming allows you to shoot your video and then quickly decide which part of the video you want to keep and save. Or put scenes together by hitting the Pause button, allowing you to create one video clip with multiple scenes.

Do you want to shoot in 2D? Quickly switch from 3D to 2D with the touch of a button. Zero in on the scene with 4x zooming in 3D and 10x zooming in 2D. And take up to sharp 16-megapixel interpolated 3D stills. Leave it to Toshiba and the CAMILEO® Z100 3D Camcorder to mak expanding your 3D world so simple and economical.

<b>Features:</b>
- 3D Videos and Stills;
- 1920x1080p Full HD Resolution videos;
- 4 megapixel 3D stills;
- 5 megapixel 2D stills - 16 megapixel (interpolated) images;
- 5 megapixel CMOS Sensor;
- Backside Illumination (BSI) - For Low Light Performance;
- 3D: 4x digital zoom;
- 2D: 10x digital zoom;
- 2.8” Glasses-free 3D Touchscreen LCD Display;
- Pause Button;
- External Microphone jack;
- SD/SDHC/SDXC card slot;
- Interfaces: mini HDMI, mini USB v2.0;
- Standard Tripod socket;
- User replaceable Lithium-Ion battery;
- File formats: MP4/H.264 (Video), JPG (images);
- Webcam (VGA) mode;
- Size: 4.7” x 2.4” x 2.1”;
- Enhanced video functions (2D): Motion Detection, Slow Motion, Time Lapse, Pre-Record;
- Enhanced video functions (3D): Pre-Record;
- Advanced photo functions (2D): Self-Timer, ISO Setting Adjustments, Date Printing, Smile Detection;
- Advanced photo functions (3D): Self-Timer, ISO Setting Adjustments, Date Printing;
