description-en_US-print:
For fantastic video that doesn't tax your budget, Toshiba's pocket-size CAMILEO® B10 Full HD Camcorder is a great place to start, offering full HD quality and lots of great features for capturing life's many moments.

This compact yet highly capable camcorder ensures you’ll enjoy every last pixel of whatever’s taking place with full HD 1080p video, and razor-sharp 16MP interpolated still photos. Get better recording indoors with backside illuminated (BSI) sensor that improves low light recording performance. Hone in on the action with a 16x digital zoom, and tap into a bigscreen TV with a built-in HDMI® port.

For better flexibility, the SD card slot allows you to swap out cards and capture the fun. Now you’ll spend more time shooting and less time worrying if you can take the next shoot.

All told, the CAMILEO® B10 Full HD Camcorder lets you break into brilliant high-def video without busting the bank.
